Here are the different roles which are available for this application.
•	CCP_TEAM_ADMIN_ROLE : This user role would be able to see and cancel any teams created documents. Able to see all orders created by all user. Manage Team maintainance					
•	CCP_USER_ROLE : This User role would be able to see all Connected orders they have generated, with ability to cancel letter using the unique order ID (Letter Ref in the portal) up until 7pm that day
•	CCP_ADMIN_ROLE : This user role would be able to select team and see all orders generated for that team, with ability to view PDF and cancel letter using the unique order ID (Letter Ref in the portal) up until 7pm that day
